[node name="ChattyPlayer" type="Control"]
clip_contents = true
layout_mode = 3
anchors_preset = 0
offset_right = 320.0
offset_bottom = 256.0
script = ExtResource("1_vdit5")
script_text = ">bg black
>wait 0.5
>bg windowsxp fade 0.5
jnfr: ... Anyways, how about we head back to my place?
ru_b: Sure! I've been curious what your apartment is like.
>disappear
>bg den slide_right 0.75
ru_b: ......
jnfr, smug: Welcome to my [wave]Epic Gamer Den[/wave]
ru_b [t=2, noanim]: ......
jnfr, smug:  At a loss for words?
ru_b: It's...
?horrible:Horrible
?interesting:... Interesting
?amazing:Really cool

#horrible
ru_b: JNFR this is.... [shake]horrible.
jnfr, angry: Oh, come on, it's not THAT bad.
ru_b: You don't EAT. Why is there [shake]FOOD[/shake] in here????
jnfr: I tried doing doordash for a bit.
>goto cup

#interesting
ru_b: It's, uh, it's... interesting?
jnfr: Interesting... how?
ru_b: You have a neat collection of... items...
ru_b: Like, that, uh...
ru_b: ... Black mold?
jnfr: Thanks! I've been cultivating that one for weeks!
ru_b: And...
>goto cup

#amazing
ru_b: It's, uh,
jnfr [wide]: Ru-B tries not to gag.
jnfr [wide]: Being a robot, the fact this is an issue is impressive on JNFR's behalf.
ru_b: Really good! Nice job, with the place, jen
jnfr: Aw, thanks!
ru_b: ... Hang on,
>goto cup

#cup
>bg dencup
ru_b: Wh- were you DRINKING from this?
ru_b: The inside is... sticky???
jnfr, angry: Drin- Ru-b. I'm a robot, of course I wasn't drinking from that.
jnfr: I was using it to hold coolant!
ru_b: WHY IS YOUR COOLANT STICKY.
>bg den
jnfr, angry: Wow, judgy today, huh?"

